      <memberdef kind="function" id="classintegration_1_1Integrator_a4e7952d8dfd3f62087cd51572dcb1726_1a4e7952d8dfd3f62087cd51572dcb1726" prot="public" static="no" const="yes" explicit="no" inline="yes" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>T</type>
        <definition>T integration::Integrator&lt; T &gt;::bd_weights</definition>
        <argsstring>(int l) const</argsstring>
        <name>bd_weights</name>
        <qualifiedname>integration::Integrator::bd_weights</qualifiedname>
        <param>
          <type>int</type>
          <declname>l</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Returns the the backwards differencing coefficients. </bold> </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
Backward differentiation formula of order <formula id="138">$k+1$</formula> is given by</para>
<para><formula id="139">\begin{align*}  \frac{d}{d x}f(x)\big|_{x_i} = \frac{1}{h}\sum^{k+1}_{l=0} c_l\, f(x_{i-l}) 
\end{align*}</formula></para>
<para>The weights are related to the <computeroutput><ref refid="classintegration_1_1Integrator_a8737cc79dbcd9f53508c705ae8f09da8_1a8737cc79dbcd9f53508c705ae8f09da8" kindref="member">poly_differentiation</ref></computeroutput> weights.</para>
<para><computeroutput><ref refid="classintegration_1_1Integrator_a4e7952d8dfd3f62087cd51572dcb1726_1a4e7952d8dfd3f62087cd51572dcb1726" kindref="member">bd_weights</ref></computeroutput> returns the coefficient <formula id="140">$c_l$</formula> for given <formula id="141">$l$</formula>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>l</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><blockquote><para>Index of weight. </para>
</blockquote></para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="cntr/integration.hpp" line="346" column="5" bodyfile="cntr/integration.hpp" bodystart="346" bodyend="346"/>
      </memberdef>
