    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Class <computeroutput><ref refid="classintegration_1_1Integrator" kindref="compound">Integrator</ref></computeroutput> contains all kinds of weights for integration and differentiation of a function at equally spaced abscissae, up to a certain order k of accuray. </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
Class <computeroutput><ref refid="classintegration_1_1Integrator" kindref="compound">Integrator</ref></computeroutput> contains all kinds of weights for integration and differentiation of a function at equally spaced abscissae, up to a certain order k of accuray. In particular, the class contains coefficients for<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Gregory quadrature</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>polynomial quadrature</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>polynomial interpolation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>polynomial differentiation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>coefficients for the backwards differencing formula (BDF) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
